main(class="min-h-full bg-zinc-50")
    section(class="border-b border-zinc-200 bg-white")
        div(class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-8 sm:px-6 lg:px-8")
            div(class="flex flex-col gap-4 lg:flex-row lg:items-end lg:justify-between")
                div
                    h1(class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-normal text-zinc-950") AI 개량 요청
                    p(class="mt-2 max-w-2xl text-[13px] leading-6 text-zinc-500") 승인된 레시피를 선택하고 목적에 맞는 개량 조건을 남깁니다.
                div(class="rounded-md border border-amber-200 bg-amber-50 px-4 py-3 text-[13px] leading-6 text-amber-800") {{ policy?.message || 'AI 개량 요청은 검수 대기로 저장됩니다.' }}

    section(class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-6 px-4 py-6 sm:px-6 lg:grid-cols-[360px_1fr] lg:px-8")
        aside(class="space-y-4")
            div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white p-4")
                h2(class="text-[15px] font-semibold text-zinc-950") 대상 레시피
                form(class="mt-3 flex gap-2", (submit)="$event.preventDefault(); searchRecipes()")
                    input(type="search", [(ngModel)]="recipeQuery", name="aiRecipeSearch", class="min-h-[40px] flex-1 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 py-2 text-[13px] outline-none focus:border-emerald-600 focus:ring-1 focus:ring-emerald-600", placeholder="레시피 검색")
                    button(type="submit", class="rounded-md bg-zinc-950 px-3 text-[13px] font-semibold text-white hover:bg-zinc-800", [disabled]="searching") 검색
                div(*ngIf="loading", class="mt-4 rounded-md bg-zinc-50 p-3 text-[13px] text-zinc-500") 대상 레시피를 불러오는 중입니다.
                div(*ngIf="!loading && recipeOptions.length === 0", class="mt-4 rounded-md bg-zinc-50 p-3 text-[13px] text-zinc-500") 선택 가능한 승인 레시피가 없습니다.
                div(class="mt-4 max-h-[520px] space-y-2 overflow-auto pr-1")
                    button(*ngFor="let item of recipeOptions", type="button", class="w-full rounded-md border px-3 py-3 text-left transition", [class.border-emerald-500]="selectedRecipe && selectedRecipe.recipeVersionId === item.recipeVersionId", [class.bg-emerald-50]="selectedRecipe && selectedRecipe.recipeVersionId === item.recipeVersionId", [class.border-zinc-200]="!selectedRecipe || selectedRecipe.recipeVersionId !== item.recipeVersionId", [class.bg-white]="!selectedRecipe || selectedRecipe.recipeVersionId !== item.recipeVersionId", (click)="selectRecipe(item)")
                        div(class="flex items-center justify-between gap-2")
                            span(class="line-clamp-1 text-[13px] font-semibold text-zinc-950") {{ item.name }}
                            span(class="shrink-0 rounded-md bg-zinc-100 px-2 py-0.5 text-xs text-zinc-600") {{ item.category || '일반' }}
                        p(class="mt-1 line-clamp-2 text-xs leading-5 text-zinc-500") {{ item.summary || item.versionTitle || '대표 승인 버전' }}
                        div(class="mt-2 flex flex-wrap gap-1.5")
                            span(*ngFor="let tag of item.tags?.slice(0, 3)", class="rounded bg-zinc-100 px-2 py-1 text-xs text-zinc-600") {{ tag }}

            div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white p-4")
                h2(class="text-[15px] font-semibold text-zinc-950") 로그인 상태
                div(*ngIf="user", class="mt-3 rounded-md bg-emerald-50 p-3 text-[13px] text-emerald-800") {{ user.nickname || user.email }} 사용자로 요청합니다.
                div(*ngIf="!user", class="mt-3 space-y-3")
                    p(class="text-[13px] leading-6 text-zinc-600") 로그인 후 AI 개량 요청을 저장할 수 있습니다.
                    button(type="button", class="w-full rounded-md bg-emerald-600 px-4 py-2 text-[13px] font-semibold text-white hover:bg-emerald-700", (click)="openLogin()") 로그인

        div(class="space-y-6")
            section(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white p-4 sm:p-5")
                h2(class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-950") 개량 목적
                div(class="mt-4 grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-3")
                    button(*ngFor="let option of purposeOptions", type="button", class="rounded-md border p-4 text-left transition", [class.border-emerald-500]="form.purpose === option.value", [class.bg-emerald-50]="form.purpose === option.value", [class.border-zinc-200]="form.purpose !== option.value", [class.bg-white]="form.purpose !== option.value", (click)="selectPurpose(option)")
                        span(class="block text-[15px] font-semibold text-zinc-950") {{ option.label }}
                        span(class="mt-2 block text-xs leading-5 text-zinc-500") {{ option.description }}

            section(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white p-4 sm:p-5")
                div(class="flex flex-wrap items-start justify-between gap-3")
                    div
                        h2(class="text-lg font-semibold text-zinc-950") 요청 조건
                        p(class="mt-1 text-[13px] text-zinc-500") {{ selectedPurpose()?.description || '개량 목적에 맞는 조건을 입력합니다.' }}
                    span(class="rounded-md bg-zinc-100 px-2.5 py-1 text-xs text-zinc-600") {{ form.recipeVersionId ? '대상 선택됨' : '대상 미선택' }}
                div(class="mt-5 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2")
                    label(class="block")
                        span(class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-600") 대상 사용자
                        select([(ngModel)]="form.targetUserType", name="aiTargetUserType", class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 py-2 text-[13px] outline-none focus:border-emerald-600 focus:ring-1 focus:ring-emerald-600")
                            option(*ngFor="let item of targetUserTypes", [value]="item") {{ item }}
                    label(class="block")
                        span(class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-600") 원하는 조리 시간
                        input(type="number", min="0", [(ngModel)]="form.desiredCookingTime", name="aiDesiredCookingTime", class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 py-2 text-[13px] outline-none focus:border-emerald-600 focus:ring-1 focus:ring-emerald-600", placeholder="분 단위")
                    label(class="block")
                        span(class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-600") 제외 재료
                        input(type="text", [(ngModel)]="form.excludedIngredients", name="aiExcludedIngredients", class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 py-2 text-[13px] outline-none focus:border-emerald-600 focus:ring-1 focus:ring-emerald-600", placeholder="쉼표로 구분")
                    label(class="block")
                        span(class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-600") 알레르기
                        input(type="text", [(ngModel)]="form.allergies", name="aiAllergies", class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 py-2 text-[13px] outline-none focus:border-emerald-600 focus:ring-1 focus:ring-emerald-600", placeholder="예: 달걀, 우유")
                    label(*ngIf="isPurpose('low_sodium')", class="block")
                        span(class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-600") 나트륨 방향
                        select([(ngModel)]="form.sodiumPreference", name="aiSodiumPreference", class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 py-2 text-[13px] outline-none focus:border-emerald-600 focus:ring-1 focus:ring-emerald-600")
                            option(value="") 기본 저염
                            option(value="very_low") 가능한 더 낮게
                            option(value="balanced") 맛 균형 우선
                    label(*ngIf="isPurpose('baby_food')", class="block")
                        span(class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-600") 아기 월령
                        input(type="number", min="0", [(ngModel)]="form.babyAgeMonth", name="aiBabyAgeMonth", class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 py-2 text-[13px] outline-none focus:border-emerald-600 focus:ring-1 focus:ring-emerald-600", placeholder="개월")
                    label(*ngIf="isPurpose('baby_food')", class="block")
                        span(class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-600") 식감 방향
                        select([(ngModel)]="form.texturePreference", name="aiTexturePreference", class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 py-2 text-[13px] outline-none focus:border-emerald-600 focus:ring-1 focus:ring-emerald-600")
                            option(value="") 월령 기준
                            option(value="smooth") 곱게 갈기
                            option(value="soft_chunks") 부드러운 작은 입자
                            option(value="finger_food") 손으로 잡는 형태
                    label(class="block sm:col-span-2")
                        span(class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-600") 맛 방향
                        input(type="text", [(ngModel)]="form.tasteDirection", name="aiTasteDirection", class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 py-2 text-[13px] outline-none focus:border-emerald-600 focus:ring-1 focus:ring-emerald-600", placeholder="예: 더 고소하게, 덜 맵게, 식감은 부드럽게")
                    label(class="block sm:col-span-2")
                        span(class="text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-600") 추가 요청사항
                        textarea([(ngModel)]="form.additionalRequest", name="aiAdditionalRequest", rows="5", class="mt-1 block w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 py-2 text-[13px] outline-none focus:border-emerald-600 focus:ring-1 focus:ring-emerald-600", placeholder="세부 요청을 입력하세요")

                div(class="mt-5 rounded-md bg-zinc-50 p-4")
                    h3(class="text-[15px] font-semibold text-zinc-950") 저장 후 상태
                    p(class="mt-2 text-[13px] leading-6 text-zinc-600") {{ policy?.message || '관리자 검수 전에는 공개 레시피로 노출되지 않습니다.' }}

                div(class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-3")
                    p(class="text-xs text-red-600") {{ message }}
                    button(type="button", class="rounded-md bg-emerald-600 px-5 py-2.5 text-[13px] font-semibold text-white hover:bg-emerald-700 disabled:cursor-not-allowed disabled:bg-zinc-300", [disabled]="!canSubmit()", (click)="submit()") 요청 저장

            section(*ngIf="success", class="rounded-md border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50 p-4 sm:p-5")
                h2(class="text-lg font-semibold text-emerald-950") 요청이 저장되었습니다
                p(class="mt-2 text-[13px] leading-6 text-emerald-800") 상태: {{ success.status }} · 요청 ID: {{ success.id }}
                p(class="mt-2 text-[13px] leading-6 text-emerald-800") 관리자 검수 후 승인된 결과만 공개 레시피로 반영됩니다.
